RACE.FOOTNOTES: HOLIDAY TICKET was allowed to settle out of the gate and saved ground around the first turn, continued unhurried up the backstretch, picked up the pace around the far turn, dug in three paths wide upper stretch and edged away. NASTY EXAGGERATOR sped to the lead at the start and set a pressured pace up the backstretch, dueled inside of BRICKBAIT around the far turn, battled on upper stretch, shook free a furlong out then got denied by the winner late. BRICKBAT stalked the pace up the backstretch, dueled outside of NASTY EXAGGERATOR around the far turn, battled on upper stretch then failed to match past the eighth pole and gave way. DRINK rated just off the leaders in early stages, hustled along two wide around the far turn, came three wide into the lane and never threatened. POKER PLAY prompted the pace around the first turn and up the backstretch, weakened around the far turn and continued to tire in the drive.

DAVIDIC LINE was forwardly placed and tracked the pace setter up the backstretch, moved up into striking distance at the five sixteenth pole, sustained bid around the far turn then retreated in the lane.
